        <h2>About Children's Ministry</h2>
        <p>
          At SWBC, we believe every child matters deeply to God — and to us.
          Our Children's Ministry exists to help kids discover who Jesus is,
          what He has done for them, and how to follow Him in their everyday lives.
        </p>
        <p>
          Children ages 3–11 begin the Sunday morning service in the sanctuary
          with their families. After the worship portion of the service, they are
          dismissed to Children's Worship — a fun, age-appropriate program led
          by caring and dedicated volunteers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our Children's Ministry is led by <strong>Chris Buntain</strong>. If
