<!-- ── WHAT TO EXPECT ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Our Classes</h2>
      <p>Children are grouped by age into three classes, each designed for where they are developmentally.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-3">

      <div class="ministry-card">
        <span class="ministry-icon">🎨</span>
        <h3>Ages 3–5</h3>
        <p>
          Our youngest learners enjoy fun, games, kids worship, and basic Bible
          stories, along with Bible memory to help little ones begin to hide
          God's Word in their hearts from an early age.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ministry-card">
        <span class="ministry-icon">📖</span>
        <h3>Ages 6–8</h3>
        <p>
          This class combines games, kids worship, and an engaging Bible story
          each week, along with Bible memorization to help kids connect faith
          to everyday life in a fun and active setting.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ministry-card">
        <span class="ministry-icon">🙏</span>
        <h3>Ages 9–11</h3>
        <p>
          Older kids participate in a small group format focused on deeper
          Bible teaching and foundational truths of the faith, preparing
          them to own their faith as they grow.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

